import { Box, Grid, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

export default function Footer() {
  return (
    <Box   color= '#666'
    justifyItems={"center"} width="100%" display="flex" justifyContent="space-evenly">
        <Box>
            <Text>Popular Searchs:</Text>
        </Box>
        <Grid templateRows='repeat(2, 1fr)' templateColumns='repeat(7, 1fr)' >
            <Text>realme buds q</Text>
            <Text>xiaomi redmi 7 case</Text>
            <Text>lenevo Ip1s tws</Text>
            <Text>5g phone</Text>
            <Text>projector 4k</Text>
            <Text>mens's sports shoes</Text>
            <Text>creality ender 3</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>xiaomi mi band 5</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>led light strip</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>360s7 robot vaccum cleaner</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>amazfit gts 2</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>roborock s5 max</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>xiaomi vaccum</Text>
            <Text lineHeight={0.1}>poco x3 nfc</Text>
        </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}
